transliteration: Ki Kaaran Kounind Hainn|| Ki Rozi Dihand Hain||109||
translation: That Thou art Doer of everything. That Thou art the Giver of the means of sustenance.109.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਰਾਜਕ ਰਹੀਮ ਹੈਂ || ਕਿ, ਕਰਮੰ ਕਰੀਮ ਹੈਂ ||
transliteration: Ki Raazak Raheem Hain|| Ki Karman Dareem Hain||
translation: That Thou art the Generous Sustainer. That Thou art the Most Compassionate.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬੰ ਕਲੀ ਹੈਂ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬੰ ਦਲੀ ਹੈਂ ||੧੧੦||
transliteration: Ki Saraban Kalee Hain|| Ki Saraban Dalee Hain||110||
translation: That Thou art Omnipotent. That Thou art the Destroyer of all.110.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਮਾਨÎੈ || ਕਿ ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਦਾਨÎੈ ||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Maaniyai|| Ki Sarbattra Daaniyai||
translation: That Thou art worshipped by all. That Thou art the Donor of all.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਗੳੁਨੈ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਭੳੁਨੈ ||੧੧੧||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Gaaounai|| Ki Sarbattra Bhaounai||111||
translation: That Thou goest everywhere. That Thou residest every-where.111.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਦੇਸੈ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਭੇਸੈ ||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Desai|| Ki Sarbattra Bhesai||
translation: That Thou art in every country. That Thou art in every garb.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਰਾਜੈ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਸਾਜੈ ||੧੧੨||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Raajai|| Ki Sarbattra Saajai||112||
translation: That Thou art the King of all. That Thou art the Creator of all.112.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਦੀਨੈਂ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਲੀਨੈਂ ||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Deenai|| Ki Sarbattra Leenai||
translation: That Thou be longest to all religious. That Thou art within everyone.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਜਾ ਹੋ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਭਾ ਹੋ ||੧੧੩||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Jaaho|| Ki Sarbattra Bhaaho||113||
translation: That Thou livest everywhere. That Thou art the Glory of all. 113.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਦੇਸੈ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਭੇਸੈ ||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Desai|| Ki Sarbattra Bhesai||
translation: That Thou art in all the countries. That Thou art in all the garbs.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਕਾਲੈ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਪਾਲੈ ||੧੧੪||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Kaalai|| Ki Sarbattra Paalai||114||
translation: That Thou art the Destroyer of all. That Thou art the Sustainer of all. 114.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਹੰਤਾ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਗੰਤਾ ||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Hantaa|| Ki Sarbattra Gadtaa||
translation: That Thou destroyest all. That Thou goest to all the places.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਭੇਖੀ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਪੇਖੀ ||੧੧੫||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Bhekhee|| Ki Sarbattra Pekhee||115||
translation: That Thou wearest all the garbs. That Thou seest all. 115.

gurmukhi: ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਕਾਜੈ || ਕਿ, ਸਰਬਤ੍ਰ ਰਾਜੈ ||
transliteration: Ki Sarbattra Kaajai|| Ki Sarbattra Raajai||
translation: That Thou art the cause of all. That Thou art the Glory of all.
